org.pimslims.business.crystallization.model
Class DeepWellPlate

java.lang.Object
  org.pimslims.business.crystallization.model.DeepWellPlate

public class DeepWellPlate
    
extends java.lang.Object





Represents a deep well plate containing a crystallization screen.
Essentially it wraps the ConditionPosition information in an org.pimslims.crystallization.model.Screen,
adding a minimal amount of physical instance information of its own, e.g. the
barcode.

CM
